==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sapless
<hw>Sap"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Destitute
of sap; not juicy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def><markp>Fig.</markp>: Dry; old; husky; withered;
spiritless.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A somewhat <xex>sapless</xex> womanhood.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Lowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now <qex>sapless</qex> on the verge of death he stands.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>sapling</ent>⟦br⟧
